{"id":25001,"date":"2020-01-13T13:30:05","date_gmt":"2020-01-13T06:30:05","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=25001"},"modified":"2020-02-06T20:07:14","modified_gmt":"2020-02-06T13:07:14","slug":"pipedream-cong-cu-lien-ket-workflow-thay-the-zapier","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/usecase\/pipedream-cong-cu-lien-ket-workflow-thay-the-zapier","title":{"rendered":"Pipedream: C\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng ho\u00e1 workflow thay th\u1ebf Zapier"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\">Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u Pipedream, c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Zapier trong vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o workflow t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng ho\u00e1.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ec1n web (hay <a href=\"\/seo\/saas-la-gi\">SaaS<\/a>) \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau \u0111\u1ec3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 <a href=\"https:\/\/zapier.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Zapier (opens in a new tab)\">Zapier<\/a> l\u00e0 &#8220;the king of king&#8221; trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c li\u00ean k\u1ebft d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Zapier v\u1ec1 th\u1ecb ph\u1ea7n, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 t\u00ednh d\u1ec5 d\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t anh t\u00e0i m\u1edbi v\u1eeba gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y th\u1ecb ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Zapier trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng xa, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 <a href=\"https:\/\/pipedream.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Pipedream (opens in a new tab)\">Pipedream<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 minh ho\u1ea1 cho Pipedream, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n li\u00ean k\u1ebft <a href=\"\/out\/woocommerce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Woocomerce (opens in a new tab)\">Woocomerce<\/a> (nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft CuongThach v\u1ec1 Woocomerce) v\u1edbi M\u1eccI d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 email marketing tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t Case study.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>PipeDream l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"531\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Pipedream-platform-1024x531.png\" alt=\"Pipedream Platform\" class=\"wp-image-25060\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Pipedream-platform-1024x531.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Pipedream-platform-218x113.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Pipedream-platform-300x156.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Pipedream-platform-700x363.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Pipedream-platform-768x399.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Pipedream-platform.png 1509w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Pipedream l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u00e2n th\u1eddi h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi l\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh vi\u00ean ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 code Nodejs nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i C\u1ef0C K\u1ef2 D\u1ec4 D\u00d9NG v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n. D\u00f9 MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1eady Pipedream c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t m\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Zapier?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Pipedream so v\u1edbi Zapier \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 &#8220;tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh t\u1ef1 do&#8221; k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i TH\u1edcI GIAN TH\u1ef0C.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1c li\u00ean k\u1ebft n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft tay b\u1eb1ng Nodejs v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ed1t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Pipedream c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u d\u00f9ng Pipedream b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 <strong>API<\/strong> ho\u1eb7c <strong>Webhook<\/strong>. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n lo, \u0111a ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ec1n web hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 API ri\u00eang \u0111\u1ec3 giao ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 Webhook \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n d\u1eef li\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>\u0110\u0103ng nh\u1eadp app.:<\/strong>&nbsp;B\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Pipedream mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng (API v\u00e0 secret key).<\/li><li><strong>T\u1ea1o Workflow.:<\/strong>&nbsp;B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o th\u1eed nh\u1eefng Workflow m\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng chia s\u1ebb ho\u1eb7c t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o workflow cho ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o m\u1edbi Workflow cho ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.<\/li><li><strong>Kh\u1edbp data v\u00e0o field.:<\/strong>&nbsp;Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o xong Workflow b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd g\u1eedi th\u1eed d\u1eef li\u1ec7u t\u1eeb \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng v\u00e0 n\u1ed1i d\u1eef li\u1ec7u ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0o khung. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f3 nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1c d\u1ec5 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ed quy\u1ebft.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/dang-nhap-app.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"493\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/dang-nhap-app-1024x493.png\" alt=\"Dang Nhap App\" class=\"wp-image-25061\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/dang-nhap-app-1024x493.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/dang-nhap-app-218x105.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/dang-nhap-app-300x144.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/dang-nhap-app-700x337.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/dang-nhap-app-768x370.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/dang-nhap-app.png 1411w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>1. \u0110\u0103ng nh\u1eadp App c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3)<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Tao-Workflow-Pipedream.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"432\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Tao-Workflow-Pipedream-1024x432.png\" alt=\"Tao Workflow Pipedream\" class=\"wp-image-25062\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Tao-Workflow-Pipedream-1024x432.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Tao-Workflow-Pipedream-218x92.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Tao-Workflow-Pipedream-300x127.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Tao-Workflow-Pipedream-700x295.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Tao-Workflow-Pipedream-768x324.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Tao-Workflow-Pipedream.png 1631w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>2. T\u1ea1o workflow<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/khop-data-vao-field.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"413\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/khop-data-vao-field-1024x413.png\" alt=\"Khop Data Vao Field\" class=\"wp-image-25063\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/khop-data-vao-field-1024x413.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/khop-data-vao-field-218x88.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/khop-data-vao-field-300x121.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/khop-data-vao-field-700x283.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/khop-data-vao-field-768x310.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/khop-data-vao-field.png 1620w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>3. Kh\u1edbp data v\u00e0o field<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>N\u1ebfu \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 trong danh s\u00e1ch?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n lo, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n linh \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>T\u1ef1 vi\u1ebft code \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p quy\u1ec1n li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Nodejs<\/strong>. C\u00e1ch n\u00e0y h\u01a1i c\u0103ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac code. Kh\u00f4ng sao, h\u00e3y l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n 3 r\u1ea5t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng.<\/li><li><strong>D\u00f9ng Pipedream HTTP Request \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o li\u00ean k\u1ebft<\/strong>. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng &#8220;Authorize&#8221;, bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o header v\u00e0 body field th\u00ec m\u1edbi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng quen.<\/li><li><strong>Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Pipedream t\u1ea1o App v\u00e0 k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Action cho b\u1ea1n<\/strong>. Nghe c\u00f3 v\u1ebb v\u00f4 l\u00fd cho m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed nh\u01b0 Pipedream, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 h\u1ecd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00f2n nhanh h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed kh\u00e1c, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 4 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o. Qu\u00e1 nhanh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n cung c\u1ea5p cho h\u1ecd t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u API v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c &#8220;Authentication&#8221; v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1ea1o &#8220;Action&#8221; lu\u00f4n trong m\u1ee5c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/PipedreamHQ\/roadmap\/issues\/new?assignees=&amp;labels=app%2C+enhancement&amp;template=app---service-integration.md&amp;title=%5BAPP%5D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Pipedream APP Request (opens in a new tab)\">Pipedream APP Request<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/yeu-cau-Pipedream-tao-app.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"733\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/yeu-cau-Pipedream-tao-app-1024x733.png\" alt=\"Yeu Cau Pipedream Tao App\" class=\"wp-image-25066\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/yeu-cau-Pipedream-tao-app-1024x733.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/yeu-cau-Pipedream-tao-app-218x156.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/yeu-cau-Pipedream-tao-app-300x215.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/yeu-cau-Pipedream-tao-app-700x501.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/yeu-cau-Pipedream-tao-app-768x550.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/yeu-cau-Pipedream-tao-app.png 1221w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u00e1ch y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Pipedream t\u1ea1o App cho b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n ti\u1ec7n t\u1ea1o lu\u00f4n Action Steps<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u00ed d\u1ee5: T\u00f4i cung c\u1ea5p cho h\u1ecd t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u Moosend API v\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng link&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/moosendapp.docs.apiary.io\/#introduction\/authentication\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https:\/\/moosendapp.docs.apiary.io\/#introduction\/authentication<\/a>&nbsp;v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o 2 Action l\u00e0 &#8220;Get mailing lists&#8221; v\u00e0 &#8220;add subscriber&#8221;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Kh\u1edbp th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb webhook v\u00e0o \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng li\u00ean k\u1ebft<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ban \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 quen r\u1ed3i th\u00ec r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u d\u00f9ng Pipedream t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt \u1edf b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1eb9o \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1y th\u1eed test tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ea7n cho tr\u01b0\u1eddng (field) t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi test th\u00ec d\u1eef li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea3i v\u00e0o Webhook Pipedream v\u00e0 b\u00e1o l\u1ed7i (d\u0129 nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a n\u1ed1i data v\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1eddng).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo b\u1ea5m v\u00e0o event trong Inspection Panel c\u1ee7a Pipedream v\u00e0 copy ph\u1ea7n&nbsp;<code>body<\/code>&nbsp;trong&nbsp;<code>steps.trigger.event<\/code>&nbsp;v\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng&nbsp;<code>Copy path<\/code>&nbsp;(<code>Copy value<\/code>&nbsp;ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng khi test v\u00ec n\u00f3 c\u00f3 d\u1ea1ng schema JSON ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n hi\u1ec3u c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac d\u1eef li\u1ec7u).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1eady l\u00e0 xong.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video controls src=\"https:\/\/media.cuongthach.com\/file\/CuongThach\/khop-du-lieu-pipedream.mp4\"><\/video><figcaption>C\u00e1ch kh\u1edbp th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Pipedream<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u00fd thuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 v\u1eady, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n t\u00f4i s\u1ebd minh ho\u1ea1 m\u1ed9t Case Study l\u00e0 Woocomerce li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi <a href=\"\/out\/moosend\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Moosend (opens in a new tab)\">Moosend<\/a> khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng COD. \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m v\u00e0 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho m\u1ecdi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Case Study: Li\u00ean k\u1ebft Woocomerce v\u1edbi Moosend v\u1edbi \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng COD<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 cho ph\u00e9p kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn&nbsp;<code>Allow customers to create an account during checkout<\/code>&nbsp;trong th\u1ebb&nbsp;<strong>Account &amp; Privacy<\/strong>&nbsp;\u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi trong webhook.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/cho-phep-khach-hang-tao-tai-khoan-khi-checkout.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"456\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/cho-phep-khach-hang-tao-tai-khoan-khi-checkout-1024x456.png\" alt=\"Cho Phep Khach Hang Tao Tai Khoan Khi Checkout\" class=\"wp-image-25071\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/cho-phep-khach-hang-tao-tai-khoan-khi-checkout-1024x456.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/cho-phep-khach-hang-tao-tai-khoan-khi-checkout-218x97.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/cho-phep-khach-hang-tao-tai-khoan-khi-checkout-300x134.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/cho-phep-khach-hang-tao-tai-khoan-khi-checkout-700x312.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/cho-phep-khach-hang-tao-tai-khoan-khi-checkout-768x342.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/cho-phep-khach-hang-tao-tai-khoan-khi-checkout.png 1613w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Allow customers to create an account during checkout (Woocomerce setting)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u1ea1n \u0111ang b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c COD (Cash on Delivery).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">T\u1ea1o Workflow tr\u00ean Pipedream<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video controls src=\"https:\/\/media.cuongthach.com\/file\/CuongThach\/tao-workflow-moi-pipedream.mp4\"><\/video><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Trigger b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 &#8220;HTTP\/Webhook Trigger, sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00eam Moosend App v\u00e0o b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Moosend App v\u00e0 Deploy (l\u01b0u l\u1ea1i).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ba b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y m\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n 2 ph\u00fat l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh. R\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1 th\u00ec h\u00e3y Copy (hay g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Fork) m\u1eabu Workflow t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o s\u1eb5n v\u00e0o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng link n\u00e0y:&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/pipedream.com\/@cuongtalentccc\/woocomerce-to-moosend-them-contact-cuongthach-com-p_OKCpDW\/edit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https:\/\/pipedream.com\/@cuongtalentccc\/woocomerce-to-moosend-them-contact-cuongthach-com-p_OKCpDW\/edit<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">T\u1ea1o webhook &#8220;order created&#8221;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video controls src=\"https:\/\/media.cuongthach.com\/file\/CuongThach\/tao-webhook-trong-Woocomerce.mp4\"><\/video><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n v\u00e0o <strong>Setting &gt; Advanced &gt; Webhook &gt; Add Webhook &gt; Topic: Order Created<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi Delivery URL l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a Webhook Pipedream v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean cho webhook l\u00e0 &#8220;Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng b\u1eb1ng COD&#8221; (b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean kh\u00e1c tu\u1ef3 th\u00edch). \u00d4 secret b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ed1ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\"><strong>Kh\u1edbp th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Pipedream<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video controls src=\"https:\/\/media.cuongthach.com\/file\/CuongThach\/khop-data-cho-field-moosend.mp4\"><\/video><figcaption>V\u00ed d\u1ee5: Sendfox<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t d\u1eef li\u1ec7u nh\u00e1p t\u1eeb Woocomerce \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eeba ki\u1ec3m tra v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o d\u1eef li\u1ec7u kh\u1edbp th\u00f4ng tin.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Woocomerce kh\u00f4ng cung c\u1ea5p c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 Webhook Test cho b\u1ea1n n\u00ean c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u1ef1 v\u00e0o website m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng xong b\u1ea1n quay l\u1ea1i Pipedream \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra &#8220;webhook event&#8221; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u01b0a \u1edf Inspection Panel.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n event th\u00ec b\u1ea1n nh\u1ea5p chu\u1ed9t v\u00e0o event \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng&nbsp;<code>steps.trigger.event.body<\/code>&nbsp;v\u00e0 xem th\u00f4ng tin nh\u01b0 t\u00ean, h\u1ecd, email,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea5m &#8220;copy path&#8221; \u1edf nh\u1eefng \u00f4 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 d\u00e1n v\u00e0o Moosend.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\"><strong>Ki\u1ec3m tra workflow l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video controls src=\"https:\/\/media.cuongthach.com\/file\/CuongThach\/check-workflow.mp4\"><\/video><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa m\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9ng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng &#8220;Send Test Event&#8221; c\u1ee7a Pipedream.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9nh &#8220;Send Test Event&#8221; l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ea5m n\u00fat. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i &#8220;Copy Value&#8221; c\u1ee7a&nbsp;<code>steps.trigger.event.body<\/code>&nbsp;v\u00e0 d\u00e1n v\u00e0o. Sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea5m n\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c t\u1ef1 th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n. R\u1ea5t linh \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu sau khi b\u1ea5m n\u00fat test kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u00e1o l\u1ed7i g\u00ec th\u00ec b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o Moosend \u0111\u1ec3 xem th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam v\u00e0o hay ch\u01b0a.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i th\u00ec th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng do l\u1ed7i c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p sai 404 status. H\u00e3y ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ea1i &#8220;Connect APP&#8221;, API v\u00e0 Secret \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang hay ch\u01b0a.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n Pipedream<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>D\u00f9 Pipedream mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 workflow nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng 1.800.000 ms\/ng\u00e0y (th\u1eddi gian workflow ch\u1ea1y). b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra trong ph\u1ea7n&nbsp;<strong>Billings<\/strong>&nbsp;c\u1ee7a&nbsp;<strong>Account<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/quota-usage-cua-pipedream.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"201\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/quota-usage-cua-pipedream-1024x201.png\" alt=\"Quota Usage Cua Pipedream\" class=\"wp-image-25069\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/quota-usage-cua-pipedream-1024x201.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/quota-usage-cua-pipedream-218x43.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/quota-usage-cua-pipedream-300x59.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/quota-usage-cua-pipedream-700x137.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/quota-usage-cua-pipedream-768x151.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/quota-usage-cua-pipedream.png 1653w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Pipedream Usage l\u00e0 t\u1ed5ng 1.800.000 ms\/ng\u00e0y<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi workflow Woocomerce nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean, m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n kho\u1ea3ng 4.000ms\/l\u1ea7n. Ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 450 \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t sinh m\u1edbi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ebft.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/thoi-gian-mot-workflow-chay.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"862\" height=\"632\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/thoi-gian-mot-workflow-chay.png\" alt=\"Thoi Gian Mot Workflow Chay\" class=\"wp-image-25070\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/thoi-gian-mot-workflow-chay.png 862w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/thoi-gian-mot-workflow-chay-218x160.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/thoi-gian-mot-workflow-chay-300x220.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/thoi-gian-mot-workflow-chay-700x513.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/thoi-gian-mot-workflow-chay-768x563.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 862px) 100vw, 862px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>M\u1ed9t Workflow ch\u1ea1y nh\u01b0 Case Study tr\u00ean t\u1ed1n kho\u1ea3ng 4.850 ms\/l\u1ea7n<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ebft, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Pipedream t\u0103ng th\u00eam cho b\u1ea1n (t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a th\u1eed n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd c\u00f3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf th\u00eam nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i suy \u0111o\u00e1n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u00fa \u00fd th\u00eam l\u00e0 m\u1ed7i Workflow nh\u01b0 v\u00ed d\u1ee5 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea1y l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 4.000 ms, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea7n sau c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 400ms do l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 cache. Ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f2n h\u01a1n 450.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tu\u1ef3 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Workflow c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n m\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n ho\u1eb7c \u00edt h\u01a1n. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng workflow \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed1n 2.000ms\/l\u1ea7n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u1eefng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Pipedream h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a g\u1eb7p v\u00ec n\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. Theo t\u00f4i, n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng l\u1eafm.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a PipeDream<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n th\u00ec Pipedream s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft g\u00f3i tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed d\u00e0nh cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 cam k\u1ebft s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng g\u00ec t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin vui, b\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Pipedream ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khi doanh nghi\u1ec7p l\u1edbn m\u1ea1nh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Pipedream ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Workflow theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng gi\u1ed1ng Zapier, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &#8220;nh\u00e1nh&#8221;, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00eam c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n &#8220;n\u1ebfu&#8230; th\u00ec&#8230;&#8221; cho b\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i theo nh\u00e1nh n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 GAME CHANGER.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng th\u00eam c\u00e1c APP m\u1edbi d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o nhu c\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng th\u00ec s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n Pipedream s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 Zapier v\u1ec1 kho \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng theo th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Pipedream ch\u1ec9 host \u1edf US-East-1 nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng cho ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c kh\u00e1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ta t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 th\u1ea5y Pipedream \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ra m\u1eaft ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng Visual Workflow Builder (c\u00f3 l\u1ebd t\u00f4i s\u1ebd y\u00eau c\u1ea7u). N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 GAME CHANGER th\u1ee9 2. Khi \u0111\u00f3, Pipedream s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i Webhook, Pipedream c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Cron Scheduler Trigger gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 crawl l\u1ea5y th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng theo l\u1ecbch c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng mail trigger c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 webhook trigger, kh\u00e1 linh \u0111\u1ed9ng cho b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 Pipedream b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>RequestBin qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Pipedream.<\/li><li>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebd Workflow d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch copy URL.<\/li><li>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin public n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n (m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u1ea9n).<\/li><li>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o Action Step d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb cho c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n.<\/li><li>B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o Connection App.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p><em>\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi workflow c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u00e9!<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u Pipedream, c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Zapier trong vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o workflow t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng ho\u00e1.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":25029,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[198],"tags":[194,56],"featured_image_urls":{"full":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/pipedream-cong-cu-lien-ket-va-tu-dong-hoa-thay-the-zapier.png",1024,512,false],"thumbnail":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/pipedream-cong-cu-lien-ket-va-tu-dong-hoa-thay-the-zapier-300x150.png",270,135,true],"medium":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/pipedream-cong-cu-lien-ket-va-tu-dong-hoa-thay-the-zapier-700x350.png",7